  "name": "Remix: Remix: Code execution",
  "description": "\u003c!-- Header --\u003e\n\u003cheader class\u003d\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-10\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center gap-3\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class\u003d\"bg-blue-600 text-white p-2 rounded-md\"\u003e\n                \u003ci class\u003d\"fas fa-archive\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003ch1 class\u003d\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\"\u003eDigital Library \u0026 Archive\u003c/h1\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"text-sm text-gray-500\"\u003e\n            \u003ci class\u003d\"fas fa-lock mr-1\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e Secure Internal Access\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/header\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- Main Content --\u003e\n\u003cmain class\u003d\"flex-1 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 w-full\"\u003e\n    \n    \u003c!-- Search and Filter Bar --\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 mb-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-between items-center\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"relative w-full sm:w-96\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class\u003d\"absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none\"\u003e\n                \u003ci class\u003d\"fas fa-search text-gray-400\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cinput type\u003d\"text\" class\u003d\"block w-full pl-10 pr-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md leading-5 bg-white placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm\" placeholder\u003d\"Search archives...\"\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cbutton class\u003d\"flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50\"\u003e\n            \u003ci class\u003d\"fas fa-filter text-gray-400\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e Filter Results\n        \u003c/button\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003c!-- Navigation Tabs --\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"border-b border-gray-200 mb-8\"\u003e\n        \u003cnav class\u003d\"-mb-px flex space-x-8\" aria-label\u003d\"Tabs\"\u003e\n            \u003cbutton onclick\u003d\"openTab(\u0027documents\u0027)\" id\u003d\"btn-documents\" class\u003d\"tab-btn active whitespace-nowrap py-4 px-1 border-b-2 border-transparent font-medium text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300\"\u003e\n                \u003ci class\u003d\"fas fa-file-pdf mr-2\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e Manuscripts \u0026 Texts\n            \u003c/button\u003e\n            \u003cbutton onclick\u003d\"openTab(\u0027media\u0027)\" id\u003d\"btn-media\" class\u003d\"tab-btn whitespace-nowrap py-4 px-1 border-b-2 border-transparent font-medium text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300\"\u003e\n                \u003ci class\u003d\"fas fa-images mr-2\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e Media \u0026 Assets\n            \u003c/button\u003e\n            \u003cbutton onclick\u003d\"openTab(\u0027data\u0027)\" id\u003d\"btn-data\" class\u003d\"tab-btn whitespace-nowrap py-4 px-1 border-b-2 border-transparent font-medium text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300\"\u003e\n                \u003ci class\u003d\"fas fa-database mr-2\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e Social Data Archives\n            \u003c/button\u003e\n        \u003c/nav\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003c!-- Tab Content: Documents --\u003e\n    \u003cdiv id\u003d\"tab-documents\" class\u003d\"tab-content active\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"\u003e\n            \n            \u003c!-- Document Card --\u003e\n            \u003cdiv class\u003d\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm archive-card overflow-hidden\"\u003e\n                \u003c